<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">同样颇受大家喜爱。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天我们就要向大家推荐一家浆水鱼鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保证你们喜欢！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201007/91bfddd2d5374427b9d7530aac8ce2ef.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是一家城墙根下的小店</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看似不起眼，但它已有29岁了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板娘是商洛柞水人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1991年就在此处开了这家店面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来来往往的食客都是老一辈的老主顾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板娘也清楚的知道每个老顾客的喜好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“她不吃辣”、“她喜欢多加韭菜”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真·实打实苍蝇小馆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201007/2ced61b0c4434d4cb20dbe7187532ffb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>浆水鱼鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">店里主营的就是搅团和鱼鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">味道做法也是多种多样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喜欢吃浆水的我当然要点一份鱼鱼啦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201007/d134d7b98e1c465ea95a085668b70d68.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼鱼也称漏鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用漏勺做出像“小鱼”一样的面条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这家的鱼鱼6元一碗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201007/5b7b99cb5f974b7ea2136196a4658df6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满当当的一勺直接倒入碗中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上芹菜、韭菜和辣子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201007/77b3a96c61724e119ad41561c4f4fa1f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再舀上一勺酸爽的浆水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一碗诱人的浆水鱼鱼就诞生了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201007/17d3d95a30704f67b4432c6b1f19ca05.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光是看着就忍不住流口水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顺着碗边轻轻一吸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“小鱼”滑进嘴里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不用咀嚼，轻轻一抿就能化开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201007/91411f95d4a747aab2056d2bdcb4bbe8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼鱼中玉米的香味非常浓郁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芹菜和韭菜交织在一起的味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配上酸爽的浆水一起钻进胃中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管吃多少都不觉得烦腻</p>
<p><strong>羊血饸饹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">店里除了搅团鱼鱼还有饸饹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">趁着刚被鱼鱼打开的胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赶紧尝一份饸饹又是另一种享受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201007/0fb39c07fa604693817a8960595e01cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">饸饹提前装好每一个袋子中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然不是现压的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但做之前都要在热水中冒一遍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201007/451a05a5dc4a490ba5e3dad81372f15e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201007/cc85c72d473d4a3896b02607414cce9f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看似毫不起眼的配料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但味道却是暖心的舒服</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一碗9元的羊血饸饹中足足有4片羊血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201007/0845808c1ec74b5382fa28cb93be62e6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勐嗦一口饸饹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在大汗淋漓中感受香辣的味觉冲击</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绝对是一种享受！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201007/0c9a771aa0e94099a41acfb926b365d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每天老板娘都要做不少鱼鱼搅团</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅是为店里食客准备</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同样也供应给各大酒店和餐馆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一排排晾晒的搅团就是为他们准备的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201007/4517e153ecc84a1b914389d72f47eb6e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
